        "created_at": "2021-01-17T14:23:10.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"167459\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Interesting; I\u2019ve never really had a mouches I\u2019ve found to be ready on release; I had the 15 at a drouhin tasting a few years back and it was super tight.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>The 2017 and now 2018 are actually both very open out of the gates. The 2018 is richer, headier, and more front-loaded; the 2017 is brighter and more sensual. But both can be tasted now with pleasure.</p>",
